OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776784267
OL,3,CMet sees increase in shoplifting
OL,4,Cconvictions in areas trialling new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police is solving 50%
OL,8,Fmore shoplifting cases in areas
OL,9,Ftrialling new technology designed to
OL,10,Frapidly identify suspects.
OL,12,FTechnology allowing retailers to
OL,13,Fsubmit reports and CCTV footage
OL,14,Finstantly has been piloted in areas
OL,15,Fsuch as Lewisham and central London
OL,16,Fsince January.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
