PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776784267
OL,3,CMet sees increase in shoplifting
OL,4,Cconvictions in areas trialling new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FAccording to the Met, providing
OL,8,Fofficers with immediate access to
OL,9,Fhighquality evidence at the point of
OL,10,Freporting makes identifying repeat
OL,11,Foffenders operating across boroughs
OL,12,Feasier.
OL,14,FSince its rollout, the positive
OL,15,Foutcome rate ` defined as an arrest,
OL,16,Fcharge or conviction ` is 21.4%, which
OL,17,Fis above the Met average of 14%.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
