OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776784267
OL,3,CMet sees increase in shoplifting
OL,4,Cconvictions in areas trialling new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FLast year, the Met said it solved
OL,8,Falmost twice as many shoplifting
OL,9,Foffences and made almost 50% more
OL,10,Farrests.
OL,12,FMet deputy commissioner Matt Jukes
OL,13,Fsaid: "Cracking down on shoplifting is
OL,14,Fa clear priority for the Met.
OL,16,F"By strengthening neighbourhood teams,
OL,17,Fusing better intelligence and focusing
OL,18,Fon hotspot locations, we are arresting
OL,19,Frepeat offenders who cause the most
OL,20,Fharm to retail staff and local
OL,21,Fbusinesses.
OL,26,@uD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776784267
OL,3,CMet sees increase in shoplifting
OL,4,Cconvictions in areas trialling new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,F"We're also using new technology to
OL,8,Fwork faster and more effectively,
OL,9,Fgiving officers a much clearer picture
OL,10,Fof offending and helping build
OL,11,Fstronger cases.
OL,13,F"Where we have trialled this retail
OL,14,Fcrime technology, more than one in
OL,15,Ffive shoplifting cases are being
OL,16,Fsolved.
OL,18,F"Strong partnership with retailers is
OL,19,Fessential. When crimes are reported
OL,20,Fpromptly and CCTV is shared quickly,
OL,21,Fofficers can take decisive action."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
