OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776784267
OL,3,CMet sees increase in shoplifting
OL,4,Cconvictions in areas trialling new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FAcross London, shoplifting fell by
OL,8,F3.7% between April 1 2025 and March 31
OL,9,Fthis year, compared with the previous
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FOfficers are able to identify around
OL,13,F80% of suspects via facial recognition
OL,14,Fsoftware in cases where clear CCTV is
OL,15,Fprovided, although only one in five
OL,16,Fcases are currently submitted with
OL,17,FCCTV evidence.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
