FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776784267
OL,3,CMet sees increase in shoplifting
OL,4,Cconvictions in areas trialling new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,FMayor of London Sir Sadiq Khan said:
OL,8,F"Backed by record funding from City
OL,9,FHall, we're redoubling our efforts to
OL,10,Fcrackdown on shoplifting and
OL,11,Fantisocial behaviour across London.
OL,13,F"Advances in technology are a real
OL,14,Fgame changer ` allowing retailers and
OL,15,Fshop staff to report shoplifting
OL,16,Fincidents remotely using digital
OL,17,Fplatforms and send evidence such as
OL,18,FCCTV footage in real-time to help
OL,19,Fpolice identify culprits, make
OL,20,Farrests, and secure prosecutions.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
