PN,40507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776784267
OL,3,CMet sees increase in shoplifting
OL,4,Cconvictions in areas trialling new
OL,5,Ctechnology
OL,7,F"Latest figures show we're making
OL,8,Fprogress reducing shoplifting in
OL,9,FLondon, but there's more to do. The
OL,10,Fpolice will continue to work closely
OL,11,Fwith businesses and use plain-clothed
OL,12,Fofficers, extensive CCTV networks, and
OL,13,Fincreased visible patrols to catch,
OL,14,Farrest, and prosecute offenders,
OL,15,Fbuilding a safer London for everyone."
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
